room_title: Escape room "The Rift" by Time to Escape in Denver
room_description:
You’ve received an encoded plea for assistance.
A mysterious research facility hides deep underground performing experiments that have torn a hole in space-time.
Uncover the corruption of Stillwater Group and follow in the footsteps of the vanished researchers. 
Sit beneath a neural compliance helmet, organize the data cores, re-route power the reactor and uncover Stillwater’s secrets before you are discovered!
